<div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a3fc4,#0a1880);border-radius:16px;padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:center">
  <div style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:white;margin-bottom:6px">Want the full question bank?</div>
  <div style="font-size:.82rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);margin-bottom:14px">Unlock 22 Reading, 20 Writing & 22 Numeracy questions — full exam mode with timer and detailed gap report.</div>
